{"trip_id":"1993-france-italy-1993-rochester-guincourt-st","epigraph":{"quote":"we are looking out across a scene from a mediaeval book of hours"},"moments":[{"seq":2,"place_id":"rochester-kent-uk","lon":0.504925,"lat":51.3883811,"place":"Rochester, Kent, UK","date":"1993-07-11","role":"main_stop","quote":"This is Thomas' last trip before going to Malvern.","images":[]},{"seq":3,"place_id":"dover-kent-uk","lon":1.3134228,"lat":51.1251275,"place":"Dover, Kent, UK","date":"1993-07-11","role":"crossing_terminal","quote":"We left straight after receiving Communion to get to Dover. It was an uneventful crossing.","images":[]},{"seq":4,"place_id":"guincourt-ardennes-france","lon":4.62611,"lat":49.55736,"place":"Guincourt, Ardennes, France","date":"1993-07-11","role":"overnight_base","quote":"John + Charles loved the playground. We met a family from Newtownards.","images":[]},{"seq":5,"place_id":"thann-haut-rhin-france","lon":7.1020957,"lat":47.8101008,"place":"Thann, Haut-Rhin, France","date":"1993-07-11","role":"overnight_base","quote":"It was raining, so we all slept in the van with John between Simon + Eve. Eve got clunked once in the night with his cast.","images":[]},{"seq":6,"place_id":"lucerne-switzerland","lon":8.3058123,"lat":47.052144,"place":"Lucerne, Switzerland","date":"1993-07-11","role":"transit_stop","quote":"We drove of past Lucerne + over the St. Gottard.","images":[]},{"seq":8,"place_id":"airolo-ticino-switzerland","lon":8.6086045,"lat":46.5290309,"place":"Airolo, Ticino, Switzerland","date":"1993-07-11","role":"overnight_base","quote":"We shared 5 pizza among the 7 of us + had ice creams for supper.","images":[{"src":"media/1993-france-italy-1993-rochester-guincourt-st/A_0095_R_1.webp","w":900,"h":741,"caption":"Icy cold, earache. The St. Gottard Pass","type":"sketch"},{"src":"media/1993-france-italy-1993-rochester-guincourt-st/A_0095_R_2.webp","w":523,"h":547,"caption":"Glued cream paper within sketch","type":"ticket"}]},{"seq":9,"place_id":"lugano-switzerland","lon":8.9512275,"lat":46.0038007,"place":"Lugano, Switzerland","date":"1993-07-11","role":"main_stop","quote":"After we bumped, Charles cried the rest of the time because he thought they were going to sink.","images":[{"src":"media/1993-france-italy-1993-rochester-guincourt-st/A_0097_L_1.webp","w":900,"h":608,"caption":"View O'Camping Rivetta, Porlezza.","type":"sketch"}]},{"seq":10,"place_id":"porlezza-lombardy-italy","lon":9.1183915,"lat":46.0360715,"place":"Porlezza, Lombardy, Italy","date":"1993-07-11","role":"overnight_base","quote":"We turned off to Camping OK Porlezza + swam in Lake Piano, between Lugano + Como.","images":[]},{"seq":11,"place_id":"crema-lombardy-italy","lon":9.6847053,"lat":45.3661004,"place":"Crema, Lombardy, Italy","date":"1993-07-11","role":"main_stop","quote":"saw the Duomo with an enormous façade, much bigger than the cathedral inside. Brick, simple, dignified.","images":[]},{"seq":12,"place_id":"soncino-lombardy-italy","lon":9.8597075,"lat":45.4043663,"place":"Soncino, Lombardy, Italy","date":"1993-07-11","role":"main_stop","quote":"At Soncino we stopped by a lovely castle + moat + the boys played football with a group of local boys + girls. Friendlier people than in the morning.","images":[]},{"seq":13,"place_id":"cremona-lombardy-italy","lon":10.037038,"lat":45.2208641,"place":"Cremona, Lombardy, Italy","date":"1993-07-11","role":"overnight_base","quote":"had pizzas in a friendly restaurant where we watched them putting pizzas in the oven.","images":[{"src":"media/1993-france-italy-1993-rochester-guincourt-st/A_0098_L_1.webp","w":898,"h":900,"caption":"Soncino castle 1479","type":"sketch"},{"src":"media/1993-france-italy-1993-rochester-guincourt-st/A_0099_L_1.webp","w":600,"h":900,"caption":"CREMONA — famous violins leaflet","type":"postcard"}]},{"seq":14,"place_id":"salsomaggiore-terme-emilia-romagna-italy","lon":9.979576,"lat":44.814762,"place":"Salsomaggiore Terme, Emilia-Romagna, Italy","date":"1993-07-11","role":"transit_stop","quote":"we are looking out across a scene from a mediaeval book of hours.","images":[]},{"seq":15,"place_id":"salsomaggiore-terme-emilia-romagna-italy","lon":9.979576,"lat":44.814762,"place":"Salsomaggiore Terme, Emilia-Romagna, Italy","date":"1993-07-11","role":"overnight_base","quote":"The camp itself has 3 swimming pools, 2 shoots, a throbbing disco (until 3am) a laundrette & a very good restaurant.","images":[{"src":"media/1993-france-italy-1993-rochester-guincourt-st/A_0100_L_1.webp","w":900,"h":547,"caption":"Barn across from Arizona swimming pool","type":"sketch"},{"src":"media/1993-france-italy-1993-rochester-guincourt-st/A_0100_R_1.webp","w":900,"h":628,"caption":"House across from camping van at Arizona","type":"sketch"}]},{"seq":16,"place_id":"parma-emilia-romagna-italy","lon":10.0979869,"lat":44.6952006,"place":"Parma, Emilia-Romagna, Italy","date":"1993-07-11","role":"overnight_base","quote":"The campsite has a resident fun fair. John & Charles & Peter went on a merry-go-round yesterday & all the boys trampolined on a 10 bouncer.","images":[{"src":"media/1993-france-italy-1993-rochester-guincourt-st/A_0101_R_1.webp","w":851,"h":900,"caption":"Torrechiara, south of Parma","type":"postcard"}]},{"seq":17,"place_id":"torrechiara-emilia-romagna-italy","lon":10.2781141,"lat":44.656766,"place":"Torrechiara, Emilia-Romagna, Italy","date":"1993-07-11","role":"main_stop","quote":"It is marvellous, + I frightened the boys into better behaviour. The Camera d'Oro was beautiful.","images":[]},{"seq":18,"place_id":"berceto-emilia-romagna-italy","lon":9.9896546,"lat":44.5106079,"place":"Berceto, Emilia-Romagna, Italy","date":"1993-07-11","role":"main_stop","quote":"Inside calm, massive, alive. John lit a candle lovely arches + crisp capitals. One of the nicest churches that I've seen.","images":[{"src":"media/1993-france-italy-1993-rochester-guincourt-st/A_0102_R_1.webp","w":900,"h":462,"caption":"Entrance ticket to Torrechiara","type":"ticket"}]},{"seq":19,"place_id":"borgo-val-di-taro-emilia-romagna-italy","lon":9.765777,"lat":44.487053,"place":"Borgo Val di Taro, Emilia-Romagna, Italy","date":"1993-07-11","role":"overnight_base","quote":"John + Charles play cars with Allesandro.","images":[]},{"seq":20,"place_id":"varese-ligure-liguria-italy","lon":9.5926994,"lat":44.3760527,"place":"Varese Ligure, Liguria, Italy","date":"1993-07-11","role":"main_stop","quote":"Simon scared a rat away as he folded up the groundsheet.","images":[{"src":"media/1993-france-italy-1993-rochester-guincourt-st/A_0103_R_1.webp","w":900,"h":786,"caption":"Varese, early town planning. bridge 1519.","type":"photo"}]},{"seq":21,"place_id":"livorno-tuscany-italy","lon":10.3402239,"lat":42.7902379,"place":"Livorno, Tuscany, Italy","date":"1993-07-11","role":"transit_stop","quote":"In the afternoon we tried to camp at Livorno but there was no room.","images":[]},{"seq":22,"place_id":"sestri-levante-trigoso-liguria-italy","lon":9.4223804,"lat":44.2736765,"place":"Sestri Levante (Trigoso), Liguria, Italy","date":"1993-07-11","role":"overnight_base","quote":"ravioli with pine nuts + basil - delicious.","images":[]},{"seq":23,"place_id":"rapallo-liguria-italy","lon":9.2316102,"lat":44.3492083,"place":"Rapallo, Liguria, Italy","date":"1993-07-11","role":"main_stop","quote":"The shopowner asked Simon whether he was the boys' father or big brother.","images":[]},{"seq":24,"place_id":"cuneo-piedmont-italy","lon":7.5581367,"lat":44.4580704,"place":"Cuneo, Piedmont, Italy","date":"1993-07-11","role":"overnight_base","quote":"Some of the loos were incredibly old + corrugated + smelled of pigs.","images":[]},{"seq":25,"place_id":"saluzzo-piedmont-italy","lon":7.494224,"lat":44.684313,"place":"Saluzzo, Piedmont, Italy","date":"1993-07-11","role":"transit_stop","quote":"We played ping pong + set off towards les Deux Alps. We stopped to shop at Saluzzo.","images":[]},{"seq":26,"place_id":"les-deux-alpes-isere-france","lon":6.1237609,"lat":45.0099949,"place":"Les Deux Alpes, Isère, France","date":"1993-07-11","role":"overnight_base","quote":"Everyone put on trousers, except Eve who didn't have any. Cold, cold.","images":[]},{"seq":27,"place_id":"grenoble-isere-france","lon":5.7357819,"lat":45.1875602,"place":"Grenoble, Isère, France","date":"1993-07-11","role":"transit_stop","quote":"At 12.15. we left + passed Grenoble + ploughed through Lyons in the rush hour.","images":[]},{"seq":28,"place_id":"lyon-france","lon":4.8320114,"lat":45.7578137,"place":"Lyon, France","date":"1993-07-11","role":"main_stop","quote":"ploughed through Lyons in the rush hour. At the last minute we visited the Fracastos + swam, + they gave us a delicious barbequed supper.","images":[]},{"seq":29,"place_id":"saint-jean-de-vaux-saone-et-loire-france","lon":4.6991922,"lat":46.8088442,"place":"Saint-Jean-de-Vaux, Saône-et-Loire, France","date":"1993-07-11","role":"overnight_base","quote":"A gorgeous vingard runs down right to the edge of the campsite. rocky outcrop above! Famous wine names all around.","images":[{"src":"media/1993-france-italy-1993-rochester-guincourt-st/A_0108_L_1.webp","w":900,"h":895,"caption":"Well + bench.","type":"sketch"},{"src":"media/1993-france-italy-1993-rochester-guincourt-st/A_0108_L_2.webp","w":799,"h":564,"caption":"entrance to courtyard.","type":"sketch"},{"src":"media/1993-france-italy-1993-rochester-guincourt-st/A_0108_R_1.webp","w":684,"h":853,"caption":"Window at side of church.","type":"sketch"}]},{"seq":30,"place_id":"lumbres-pas-de-calais-france","lon":2.12179,"lat":50.7051363,"place":"Lumbres, Pas-de-Calais, France","date":"1993-07-11","role":"overnight_base","quote":"John + Charles got filthy in the play ground.","images":[]},{"seq":31,"place_id":"calais-france","lon":1.8538446,"lat":50.9524769,"place":"Calais, France","date":"1993-07-11","role":"crossing_terminal","quote":"Set off on a long drive up towards Calais 12.00.","images":[]},{"seq":32,"place_id":"dover-kent-uk","lon":1.3134228,"lat":51.1251275,"place":"Dover, Kent, UK","date":"1993-07-11","role":"crossing_terminal","quote":"Set off on a long drive up towards Calais 12.00.","images":[{"src":"media/1993-france-italy-1993-rochester-guincourt-st/A_0110_R_1.webp","w":508,"h":900,"caption":"Watertower Outside E.Leclerc near Chalons s. Saone","type":"sketch"}]}]}